        <heading>Property Tax Assessment</heading>
        <section eId="sec_12_62a">
          <num>12-62a</num>
          <heading>Uniform assessment date and rate</heading>
          <subsection eId="12_62a__subsec_a">
            <num>(a)</num>
            <content>
              <p>Each municipality, as defined in section7-381, shall establish a uniform assessment date of October first.</p>
            </content>
          </subsection>
          <subsection eId="12_62a__subsec_b">
            <num>(b)</num>
            <content>
              <p>Each such municipality shall assess all property for purposes of the local property tax at a uniform rate of seventy per cent of present true and actual value, as determined under section12-63.</p>
            </content>
          </subsection>
